<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://blog.i18n.ro/are-we-supposed-to-localize-keyboard-shortcuts/" class="external free" title="http://blog.i18n.ro/are-we-supposed-to-localize-keyboard-shortcuts/" rel="nofollow">http://blog.i18n.ro/are-we-supposed-to-localize-keyboard-shortcuts/</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> For the current list see <a href="http://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php" class="external text" title="http://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php" rel="nofollow">KDE.org</a></li>
</ol>
